data.description: Welcome to this 5 year young, END UNIT townhome. Experience maintenance free living with the luxury of having end unit privacy. This home offers 2 bedrooms, 1.5 baths, and a HUGE upper level loft/additional living area! The Main bedroom offers a walk in closet and upper level laundry room right around the corner. A great place to settle in right across from Oak Hill Elementary. Sellers are offering buyers $3,000 for fresh coat of paint or a RATE BUY DOWN!!
